en_628311_0	The new Commander Security Forces - Jaffna, Major General Ruwan Wanigasooriya made his maiden field visit to the 51 Division Headquarters in Kopai on Thursday (18).
en_628311_1	After the Security Forces Commander was warmly welcomed by the General Officer Commanding 51 Division, he was honoured in a Guard Turnout and a parade in accordance with military traditions.
en_628311_2	Afterwards, Brigadier Lalith Ratnayake, General Officer Commanding, 51 Division presented a comprehensive briefing on the role and tasks of the 51 Division as well as its projects on reconciliation and community welfare.
en_628311_3	Afterwards, the Security Forces Commander addressed the troops and the gathering of Senior Officers and Staff Officers.
